### Get All Tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get All Tasks - Filter by Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?status=TODO
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get All Tasks - Filter by Priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?priority=HIGH
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get All Tasks - Filter by Status and Priority
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?status=IN_PROGRESS&priority=URGENT
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get All Tasks - Filter by Assigned User
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks?assignedToId=2
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Task by ID
@taskId = 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Task by ID - Invalid ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Task by ID - Not Found
GET {{baseUrl}}/tasks/9999
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

